ThermalTrap(8)              System Manager's Manual             ThermalTrap(8)

NAME
     ThermalTrap – system application for presenting thermal warnings.

DESCRIPTION
     ThermalTrap is a system application that notifies the user when the
     system temperature exceeds usable limits.

     There are no options for ThermalTrap, and users should not run
     ThermalTrap manually.

